      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in wonderful shape, making it the perfect choice for someone who wants a smooth, dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road with you today! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
