      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb mechanical specimen for the serious driver. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, facilitated by its signature individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers tactile, short-throw shifts, while the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, ensuring the high-pressure variable valve timing operates within factory tolerances. Equipped with a functional limited-slip differential and a suspension geometry that remains tight and communicative, this car offers the quintessential analog driving experience. It shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with its well-maintained status, but remains a turn-key performance machine.",
